sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant Client as React Client
  participant Store as Redux Store
  participant API as Express API
  participant DB as SQLite via TypeORM

  User->>Client: Click History
  Client->>Store: fetchSavedPeople
  Store->>API: GET /api/people
  API->>DB: repository.find
  DB-->>API: saved profiles
  API-->>Store: saved profiles
  User->>Client: Update or Delete profile
  Client->>API: PATCH or DELETE /api/people/:id
  API->>DB: repository.save or repository.delete
  DB-->>API: result
  API-->>Client: updated profile or 204
